Energy Development of Philippines Rises to Record as First Gen Buys Shares

-- B y   I a n   S a y s o n
-- 
2011-04-04T01:53:12Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-04-04/energy-development-of-philippines-rises-to-record-as-first-gen-buys-shares.html
Energy Development Corp. (EDC)  climbed to
a record in Manila trading after parent First Gen Corp. said it
exercised an option to buy more than 390 million shares in the
unit.  Energy Development surged 5.7 percent to 6.65 pesos as of
9:40 a.m. local time, set for the highest close since the stock
began trading in December 2006. First Gen advanced 1.6 percent
to 13 pesos, the highest since Nov. 15.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Ian Sayson in Manila at 
 isayson@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Reinie Booysen at 
 rbooysen@bloomberg.net  